How to revert from Working directory
      git checkout filename
      git checkout *

How to discard from staging/index area
      git reset filename
      git reset *

How to Revert from Repository
      git reset HEAD~1
      git reset HEAD~3

How to remove from All three working/index/Repository
      git reset HEAD~2 --hard

How to remove from staging and Repository
      git reset HEAD~3   (By default mode is mixed)

How to remove from Repository only
      git reset --soft HEAD~2

How to revert from Remote
      git revert commitid
